te=2009-07-07|archive-date=2009-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090710021512/http://www.fastcompany.com/blog/clay-dillow/culture-buffet/twitter-revolution-lives-china-disables-twitter-then-facebook-civil-|dead-url=no}}</ref>
